“For the demos, I’m going to use sanitized examples and lab-safe commands.

Some commands in this deck can restart services, change firewall rules, or delete files. When I show those, I’ll either use a safe path under /tmp, or I’ll use echo to show what the command would look like without actually making the change.

The main rule for the demos is simple: move fast, but make the safe path your default.”

